OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FHealth Correspondent Helen Ford went
OL,8,Fto meet Matt Smith, who has suffered
OL,9,Ffrom migraines since he was 16
OL,11,FA man who has suffered debilitating
OL,12,Fmigraine attacks for 20 years has
OL,13,Fwelcomed the approval of a new drug,
OL,14,Fdedicated specifically to deal with
OL,15,Fthe condition.
