OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FMatt Smith, from North Tyneside, told
OL,8,FITV Tyne Tees he had given up on
OL,9,Fgetting medication - which is often
OL,10,Fintended for other conditions - for
OL,11,Fhis migraine attacks, due to severe
OL,12,Fside effects.
OL,14,FFor Matt, his migraines have at times
OL,15,Fbeen so bad he lost vision in both
OL,16,Feyes, and recovery took up to a week
OL,17,Fdue to slow-to-subside facial pain.
