OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FA new treatment, which could become
OL,8,Favailable on the NHS, could be a light
OL,9,Fat the end of the tunnel for the 35-
OL,10,Fyear-old.
OL,12,FThe new drug Atogepant - sold under
OL,13,Fthe brand name Aquipta and made by
OL,14,FAbbVie - has been given the green
OL,15,Flight for NHS use under new final
OL,16,Fdraft guidance from the National
OL,17,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,18,FExcellence (Nice).
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
