OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FThe once-a-day tablet could only be
OL,8,Fprescribed by specialists and for
OL,9,Fpeople who have unsuccessfully tried
OL,10,Fat least three other treatments for
OL,11,Fmigraines.
OL,13,FMatt, who has suffered from migraine
OL,14,Fattacks since he was 16, described the
OL,15,Fcondition as a "continuous grind".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
