OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,F"It's quite a debilitating condition
OL,8,Fand a lonely condition," he said.
OL,9,F"It's something that is always there
OL,10,Fand is always in the background and as
OL,11,Fyou go through trying to live your
OL,12,Flife...it gives you almost a constant
OL,13,Fbattle with yourself in terms of being
OL,14,Fable to function at a level that you
OL,15,Fwould like to."
OL,17,FMatt's attacks peaked during the
OL,18,Fpandemic, when he was experiencing
OL,19,Fthem for up to 20 days a month.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
