OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FHe tried several treatments but -
OL,8,Fbecause some were originally intended
OL,9,Ffor other conditions - he found the
OL,10,Fside effects debilitating.
OL,12,FHe added: "Throughout, obviously the
OL,13,Fnumber of years, I've tried a number
OL,14,Fof different things the GP has offered
OL,15,Fand you almost feel like a bit like a
OL,16,Flab rat in terms of being able to
OL,17,Funderstand how it would work for you
OL,18,Fto the point where, late twenties, I
OL,19,Fjust gave up in terms of medication."
