OL,7,FAbout 10 million adults in the UK are
OL,8,Fthought to have experienced or live
OL,9,Fwith migraine, with about one in five
OL,10,Fwoman and one in twelve men affected.
OL,12,FThe condition can be severe and can
OL,13,Fimpact sufferers' ability to work,
OL,14,Fsocialise and care for dependents, and
OL,15,Fcan take a toll on their mental health.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
