OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FThe new treatment would only be
OL,8,Favailable to people who have at least
OL,9,Ffour migraine days each month and have
OL,10,Ftried at least three other treatments
OL,11,F- offering a new choice for an
OL,12,Festimated 170,000 patients in England.
OL,14,FMatt said: "It would give people hope
OL,15,Fin terms of having something specific
OL,16,Ffor the condition. It's meant to
OL,17,Ftackle symptoms and causes people have.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
