OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,F"People do struggle with this daily.
OL,8,FThere's no scope to be able to say I
OL,9,Fcan't work for that many hours or days
OL,10,Fin a week. A lot of people have to
OL,11,Fgrin and bear it. it's quite well
OL,12,Fhidden - you can struggle in silence.
OL,14,F"If it can help people live in a bit
OL,15,Fmore comfort and not having severe
OL,16,Fpain that's fantastic."
OL,18,FRob Music, from the Migraine Trust,
OL,19,Fsaid: "For too many years, migraine
OL,20,Fhas been very much left to the one
OL,21,Fside and not taken seriously.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
