OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,F"We are seeing changes now. That's
OL,8,Fgreat. So great there's a new
OL,9,Ftreatment but it's only great if the
OL,10,Fpeople who need it, who deserve it can
OL,11,Faccess it as soon as they possibly can
OL,12,Fand that's the bit that must change."
OL,14,FLast year, the Bishop Auckland MP
OL,15,FDehenna Davison
OL,17,FWelcoming the new treatment, she told
OL,18,FITV News: "I raised this in parliament
OL,19,Frecently and the first parliamentary
OL,20,Fdebate on migraine since the 1960s
OL,21,Fwhich in itself is kind of baffling.
