OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,F"I'm going to be discussing this with
OL,8,Fthe minister to see how we can get
OL,9,Fthese drugs to people faster because
OL,10,Fso many people who do access them say
OL,11,Fthey can be life changing."
OL,13,FIf there are no appeals against its
OL,14,Ffinal draft guidance, Nice is expected
OL,15,Fto publish its final guidance on the
OL,16,Fdrug next month.
