OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FHealth Minister Andrew Stephenson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Migraines affect millions of
OL,9,Fpeople in this country and this new
OL,10,Ftreatment will help prevent recurring
OL,11,Fmigraine attacks when other medicines
OL,12,Fhave failed.
OL,14,F"It will allow more people whose daily
OL,15,Flife is affected by this painful,
OL,16,Fdebilitating condition to manage their
OL,17,Fmigraines more effectively and to live
OL,18,Ftheir lives to the fullest."
